# Siemens S7-1500 OT Template Standard
# Import to TIA Portal — File: FB_CycleMaster.scl
# 
# Handshake protocol:
# 1. PLC sets CycleReady = TRUE when cycle complete
# 2. Python reads CycleLog data structure
# 3. Python sets CycleReset = TRUE (acknowledge)
# 4. PLC clears CycleReady and CycleReset
#
# Timestamp is calculated by PLC (using RD_SYS_T), not by Python.
# This ensures ≤10ms accuracy independent of network.

